title: Week 15 NFL Recap with the NFL Friends (Football 12/17)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Ryan Wilson, John Breech and Sean Wagner-McGough to break down all the biggest stories from Sunday's Week 15 NFL action including Patriots-Steelers (2:00), Eagles-Rams (13:00), Colts-Cowboys (35:00), Ravens Buccaneers (41:00), who might trade for Joe Flacco (45:00), Dolphins-Vikings (51:00), Seahawks-49ers (56:00), Titans-Giants (1:00:45), Redskins-Jaguars (1:05:30), Lions-Bills (1:07:15), Raiders-Bengals (1:08:30) and Cardinals-Falcons (1:09:45).
